<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201103/fb522ec338484cd39d25fd9a29c3d401.jpeg" width="640" height="420" /></p>
<p><strong>好消息iPhone 12 mini/Pro Max将提前接受预订</strong></p>
